sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Anki
    participant Browser
    participant Visibility as field_visibility.py
    participant Config
    participant DOM as Editor DOM

    User->>Anki: Open Browser
    Anki->>Browser: Create Browser window
    Browser-->>Anki: Browser ready

    User->>Browser: Select note
    Browser->>Visibility: editor_will_load_note(...)
    Visibility->>Config: Read visibility settings
    Visibility-->>Browser: Return hide/reset JS
    Browser->>Visibility: apply_field_visibility(editor)
    Visibility->>Config: Read visibility settings
    Visibility->>DOM: Hide non-allowed fields

    User->>Browser: Click Show Fields
    Browser->>Visibility: toggle_field_visibility(editor)
    Visibility->>Config: Disable hiding for note type
    Visibility->>DOM: Reset visibility
    Visibility-->>Browser: Update button label

    User->>Browser: Click Hide Fields
    Browser->>Visibility: toggle_field_visibility(editor)
    Visibility->>Config: Re-enable hiding for note type
    Visibility->>DOM: Apply hide JS again
    Visibility-->>Browser: Update button label
